Maharashtra
Sep 29, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			Railway employee Raju Marshettiwar, 55, was arrested for allegedly forcing himself upon a 2-and-a-half-year-old girl in Sadar. Sadar police booked Marshettiwar for rape when the minor girl complained of injury to her private parts on Tuesday. Her mother took her for treatment after the girl told her that Marshettiwar had misbehaved with her while she was playing near his house on September 20.